	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You emit powerful radiant energy from your body, channeling the power of the sun to burn your enemies.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - Enemies in a 60 ft. Radius - 1 Minute - 1/Long Rest - Magical</p><ul><li><p>When you use this ability, you begin emitting bright light in a 30 ft. radius and dim light in a 60 ft. radius, which counts as sunlight. When you use this ability, and again on each of your turns as a bonus action, you can deal damage to your enemies.</p></li></ul><p><strong>[[/save con]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 20 radiant]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> [[/damage 10 radiant]] damage.</p></li></ul>",
